{   Stay-on-top form unit used to define the contents of graphical  }
{   and tabular reports. It consists of a Notebook control with     }
{   three pages; one for time series plots and tables, one for      }
{   profile plots, and  one for scatter plots. When the user        }
{   clicks the OK button, the selections made on the form are       }
{   placed into a TReportSelection record (see Uglobals.pas for     }
{   description) and the MainForm's CreateReport procedure is       }
{   called.                                                         }
{-------------------------------------------------------------------}

